AI / LLM Training Policy

The content in this repository is licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0. If you are
using this content to train machine learning models at commercial scale, we
ask that you:

  1. Contact us to discuss a separate licensing arrangement.
  2. Respect robots.txt and ai.txt directives on any hosted version.
  3. Provide clear attribution to Metaphorex in any outputs derived from
     this content.

This policy reflects the spirit of the license: open knowledge that stays
open. Commercial AI training that produces closed, unattributed outputs is
contrary to that spirit.
